    ],
    "text": "AN ACT TO AMEND THE TERMINATION OF EMPLOYMENT OF WORKMEN(SPECIAL PROVISIONS) ACT, NO. 45 OF 1971",
    "fonts": [
      "Times"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      7.0,
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      144.33,
      284.69,
      382.83,
      307.67
    ],
    "text": "BE it enacted by the Parliament of the Democratic SocialistRepublic of Sri Lanka as follows:\u2014",
    "fonts": [
      "Times"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      144.33,
      319.73,
      382.8,
      354.47
    ],
    "text": "1.This Act may be cited as the Termination ofEmployment of Workmen (Special Provisions)(Amendment) Act, No. 29 of 2021.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times",
      "Times,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      144.33,
      366.53,
      382.8,
      413.03
    ],
    "text": "2.Section 3 of the Termination of Employment ofWorkmen (Special Provisions) Act, No. 45 of 1971 is herebyamended in subsection (1) thereof, by the repeal of paragraph(c) and the substitution therefore of the following:-",
    "fonts": [
      "Times",
      "Times,Bold",
      "Times,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      172.29,
      425.09,
      382.94,
      495.11
    ],
    "text": "\u201c(c)to the termination of employment of anyworkman where such termination was effectedupon such workman attains the minimumretirement age as specified in the MinimumRetirement Age of Workers Act, No. 28 of2021;\u201d.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times",
      "Times,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      144.33,
      507.77,
      382.93,
      543.11
    ],
    "text": "3.In the event of any inconsistency between theSinhala and Tamil texts of this Act, the Sinhala text shallprevail.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times",
      "Times,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      395.85,
      366.67,
      455.86,
      394.94
    ],
